text: Khumoyunmirzo Iminov (Uzbek Cyrillic: Хумоюнмирзо Иминов; born 15 January 2000) is an Uzbekistani footballer who currently plays as a midfielder for Energetik-BGU Minsk on loan from Pakhtakor Tashkent.
